Package address.data

Class AddressEntry

java.lang.Object
address.data.AddressEntry
public class AddressEntry
extends java.lang.Object
Represents a single object entry in the AddressBook class Overrides a toString() method that prints out all the data in an entry
Since:
February 2021
Author:
Tey Jon Sornet
